      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. To help our design team with the actual product imagery and model selection, could you break that down a bit more by demographic? Like, if we're looking at different major groups—European, East Asian, African, etc.—what are the specific facial features that are usually considered the 'gold standard' for each? We want to make sure we're hitting those specific ideals for each market.",
